sequenceDiagram
    participant Producer as External Producer
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP
    participant AP as Async Processor<br/>(N=8 workers)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP
    participant IGW as Inference Gateway<br/>80/443 TCP
    participant Consumer as External Consumer

    Note over Producer,Consumer: Flow 1: Async Inference Request (Redis Sorted Set)

    Producer->>Redis: ZADD request queue<br/>(score=deadline, Redis protocol)<br/>Optional TLS, URL credentials
    AP->>Redis: ZPOPMIN request queue<br/>(poll for next job)<br/>Optional TLS, URL credentials

    Note over AP: RandomRobinPolicy merges<br/>multiple queue channels

    AP->>Prom: GET PromQL query<br/>HTTP/9090 (no TLS)<br/>Check dispatch gate budget
    Note over AP: Gate evaluates:<br/>D = max_SYS - running - queue_size<br/>if D > baseline → dispatch

    AP->>IGW: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP(S) 80/443<br/>TLS 1.2+ / optional mTLS<br/>Header: x-gateway-inference-objective

    alt Success (2xx)
        IGW-->>AP: 200 OK (inference result)
        AP->>Redis: LPUSH result queue<br/>Optional TLS, URL credentials
        Consumer->>Redis: BRPOP result queue<br/>Optional TLS, URL credentials
        Redis-->>Consumer: Inference result

    else Rate Limited (429) or Server Error (5xx)
        IGW-->>AP: 429/5xx response
        Note over AP: Exponential backoff:<br/>jitter in [temp/2, temp)<br/>capped at 60s<br/>Respects Retry-After header

        AP->>Redis: ZADD request queue<br/>(re-enqueue with backoff score)<br/>Optional TLS, URL credentials
        Note over AP: Next poll cycle picks up<br/>retried request via ZPOPMIN

    else Deadline Exceeded
        Note over AP: Request deadline passed<br/>Drop request, log error
        AP->>Redis: LPUSH result queue<br/>(error result with deadline_exceeded)
    end

    Note over Producer,Consumer: Flow 2: Async Inference Request (GCP Pub/Sub)

    participant GCP as GCP Pub/Sub<br/>443/TCP

    Producer->>GCP: Publish to request topic<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>GCP IAM auth
    GCP->>AP: Receive subscription message<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth2 credentials

    AP->>Prom: GET PromQL query<br/>Check dispatch gate
    AP->>IGW: POST inference request<br/>HTTP(S) 80/443

    alt Success
        IGW-->>AP: 200 OK
        AP->>GCP: Publish to result topic<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth2 credentials
    else Failure
        Note over AP: Nack message for redelivery
    end

    Note over AP: Graceful Shutdown

    Note over AP: Context cancelled →<br/>1. Re-enqueue in-flight requests<br/>2. Flush pending retries<br/>3. Drain result channel<br/>4. Release quota (sync.Map)<br/>5. Wait drainWg (130s grace)
